---
/* Arsenal Section — "Ce qui est inclus" | Light Editorial */
---

<section id="arsenal" class="bg-surface-container py-[var(--spacing-section-gap)]">
  <div class="container-main">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start mb-16 gap-8">
      <div class="reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">Ce qui est inclus</span>
        <h2 class="font-display text-[length:var(--font-size-h1)] font-bold tracking-tight text-on-surface mt-4 normal-case">
          Ton arsenal complet
        </h2>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-lg max-w-md mt-3">
          Rien n'est laissé au hasard pour te rendre opérationnel.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal delay-1">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-white border border-primary/20 rounded-full text-primary text-sm font-sans font-bold tracking-wider">
          Valeur totale : +5&nbsp;000&euro;
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 6-card grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 border border-outline-variant/20 reveal delay-1">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5" aria-hidden="true">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">inventory_2</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-on-surface text-lg mb-3 normal-case">Formation Make Complète</h3>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed"><strong>De zéro à expert</strong>. Scénarios avancés, APIs, webhooks, architecture.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 border border-outline-variant/20 reveal delay-2">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5" aria-hidden="true">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">device_hub</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-on-surface text-lg mb-3 normal-case">Formation n8n Complète</h3>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">Workflows <strong>open-source</strong>, <strong>self-hosted</strong>. Déploie sans limites.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 border border-outline-variant/20 reveal delay-3">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5" aria-hidden="true">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">videocam</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-on-surface text-lg mb-3 normal-case">2 Lives par Semaine</h3>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed"><strong>Sessions tactiques en groupe</strong> pour débloquer tes blocages en temps réel.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 border border-outline-variant/20 reveal delay-4">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5" aria-hidden="true">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">person</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-on-surface text-lg mb-3 normal-case">Coaching 1-to-1</h3>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed"><strong>2h de session individuelle</strong> avec Lilian pour aligner ta trajectoire.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 border border-outline-variant/20 reveal delay-5">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5" aria-hidden="true">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">bar_chart</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-on-surface text-lg mb-3 normal-case">SaaS de Pilotage</h3>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">Accès à notre <strong>outil interne</strong> pour gérer ta trésorerie freelance.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 border border-outline-variant/20 reveal delay-6">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5" aria-hidden="true">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">call</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-on-surface text-lg mb-3 normal-case">Call Expert-Comptable</h3>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">30 min avec un <strong>expert-comptable</strong> pour structurer ton activité.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
